    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculties behaviour while teaching,they are very generous,helpful.",
          "name": "Sonia Baidya",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "As this is a research institute, IISER Bhopal does not have a significant number of students getting placed into companies from natural sciences. However, there is a good number of Ph.D. placements made from here.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lab Facilities and their quality. Top-grade equipments are provided.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus Life. There are many activities and events happening, resulting in a very lively campus.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Junior-Senior Interactions. There is no ragging on campus, and seniors are very helpful and not authority exerting.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The professors are great at their subjects, most of them are chill and very approachable",
          "name": "Prakhar Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placements happen mainly for engineering sciences and economic sciences students. Most of the BS-MS student opt for higher studies over placement. The campus is quite new with almost all research, academic, sports etc facilities.",
          "name": "Veeru Kumar Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The course curriculum is relevant to the industry and research based rather than theoretical or based only.",
          "name": "Veeru Kumar Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Sports are in the wide area to play the games and all kind of sports will be available to relife the stress and there is also gym available in the IISER Bhopal",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Amazing sports facilities,with dedicated coaches for each sport",
          "name": "Rudra Prasad Tarai",
          "course_tag_name": "BS"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Sometimes the way of teaching.Teachers should understand how to teach that students can understand.",
          "name": "Sonia Baidya",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no night canteen and both the market complex and everything to shop closes before 12am. only vending machine left in some hostels and that too empty at night mostly.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "many students come here choosing this as a backup which ruins the quality of peers sometimes.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The placement cell is not developed completely and very few companies gather here for recruitment.",
          "name": "Veeru Kumar Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no coding culture of his institute,hat you generally find in other engineering colleges,but efforts are made from the student side to develop the same",
          "name": "Rudra Prasad Tarai",
          "course_tag_name": "BS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Very bad placements for now.hope the scenario will improve in upcoming years",
          "name": "Rudra Prasad Tarai",
          "course_tag_name": "BS"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is only a primary health centre in the campus which caters to basic needs and for any serios injury(caused by playing sports), we have to travel far away hospitals.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The academic section is not lenient and not very cooperative and so it gets difficult for the students to manage everything. Although it's part of learning and gaining experiences, it comes at the cost of missing few classes.",
          "name": "Kunalika Adweta",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Events are not upto expectations and mostly delayed",
          "name": "Saurav",
          "course_tag_name": "BS"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
